Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:04.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all\nthe shards of the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:08.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku with my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:12.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As though lured by the Sacred Jewel shards,\nwe continue our search.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sesshomaru is assailed\nby Jakotsu and Suikotsu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:18.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and two dead mortals,\NBankotsu and Kikyo, meet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's up to us and Miroku,\NSango, Shippo and Kirara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:22.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Travel back in time for\na Feudal Fairy Tale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:23.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:12.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mt. Hakurei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am certain that Naraku is there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:20.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kyokotsu, {\i1}Mukotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:41.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How does it feel to be\nback in that world again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:48.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once you're dead, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This man...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you're one of\nthe Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:04.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:08.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:14.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku never told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard the stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I never thought you'd be\nthis pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:26.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:47.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This one's Sacred Jewel shards\nexude tainted black light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}unlike Suikotsu's clear one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:53.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean he has been completely\novertaken by the dark?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well? Aren't you going to shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you intend to do\nin this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you continue to kill\neven after being resurrected?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What reason do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that's a strange question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't need a reason to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've always been this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In death, and after\NI was resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:22.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the world we live in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:26.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it's sometimes necessary to kill\nin order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:31.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you died once. So why not\ntry to change the way you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:37.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I'm a mercenary to the core.\NAnd I enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,People talk about heaven and hell.\NBut once you're dead, you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:52.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't care about the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While I live, I'll do as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:02.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You say that to convince yourself, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're trying to make excuses\nfor what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:10.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,dead people like us will probably\nshare the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:18.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you should worry about\nyourself instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}whatever....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us both live as long\nas we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:34.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The fate of the {\i1}dead....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One of Naraku's followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How perceptive of {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like that poison user,\nyou smell like the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow....{\i0}\NYou have a sharp sense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:06.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What I'd expect from\NInuyasha's older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:18.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silly human!\NStay still and be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey dwarf, didja say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Dwarf"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:29.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's get away from here, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:34.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're of no help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're only in Lord Sesshomaru's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:46.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} You don't want the girl\nin harm's way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh! You talk a lot for\na dead person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit harping on and on\nabout me being dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:08:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But now, you won't hold back\nwhen you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope Lord Sesshomaru will\nbe all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool, Lord Sesshomaru would\nnever fall to a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You might though, Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you!\NI am a demon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:22.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way will I lose\nto a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:42.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He looks strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look away and your head\nwill fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get back, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:07.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If anything happens to Rin,\NLord Sesshomaru will kill me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:08.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Staff of Two Heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:23.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did I get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err....Jaken, the bridge will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that!\NRun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't be killed so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:40.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Rin!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:51.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard that girl was\nhis weak point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:01.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My plan was to kidnap the kid\nand use her as a hostage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never thought he'd leave his\nback wide open for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that! And that! And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gotcha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He deflected my Jakotsu sword\nand sent it back at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn. I barely missed\nkilling him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, he's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:51.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Couldn't die in peace if I'm killed by\NInuyasha's brother before I kill Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:55.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How far are we going, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who knows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:11.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm just carrying this puny wolf to\na safe enough place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Safe place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Band of Seven are\nafter Koga's Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:20.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who knows when they'll come\nafter him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:26.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You heard him, Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was carried away\nby the river.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The water is washing away\nher smell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:57.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you pretending to be dead, Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:06.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ohhh....{\i0}\NPlease forgive me, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:10.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it kills me, I shall find Rin and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:12.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's angry, after {\i1}all....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NWhy do you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:48.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not fear me.\NI am a physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:54.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's different from that other man?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:02.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. You had companions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:02.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:05.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll come looking\nfor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:09.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I shouldn't move around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This forest is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should stay with me until\nyour companions find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:22.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't seem like a bad man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:38.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:42.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No. I don't sense any\ndemonic aura either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:46.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Naraku is\nreally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:51.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we have no choice but\nto keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:58.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But being separated like this, you feel\ngrateful for Inuyasha's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:02.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's convenient to have\naround....especially with his nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:05.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we let him, he'd spend the whole night\nrunning around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:23.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango....that cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:37.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:42.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope she leaves without\nnoticing anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to fight her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:52.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a doctor in the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I live in a house at\nthe base of Mt. Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:01.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Rin, there are lots of children\nabout the same age as you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who don't have any family either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:08.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:18.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sense the presence\nof a Sacred Jewel shard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's approaching the village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:26.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's different from that\nother man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:28.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suikotsu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:33.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this presence...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:49.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure.\NImpure is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:53.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:06.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I left like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:10.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really Dr. Suikotsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-uh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:23.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This girl is Rin.\NBe nice to her, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu has returned to\nhis old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:35.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My hunch was right.\NGood thing I stuck around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:39.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well, can't be helped.\NI'll have to open his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It IS Dr. Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:49.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu, we beg of you.\NPlease leave the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:59.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wasn't it your fault that the Band of Seven\nattacked this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:03.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And your expression at that {\i1}time....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You looked like a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What ingrates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:32.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all my ministrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:43.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the same one who\nattacked us on the bridge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:47.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}l- I have to run away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can smell them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}those specters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:06.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are at the base\nof Mt. Hakurei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,L-Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:11.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It could be my imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but the barrier seems stronger\nthan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He won't answer me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:26.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this fur... feels so wonderful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The battle still continues.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:43.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To walk this path once more\nonly confirms my cursed fate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And beyond this darkness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}what awaits...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:57.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once more... just once more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:02.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ascertain the fates of\nthose men who are dead mortals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu, what's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jakotsu, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:25.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before, when you had that face,\nyou would never hurt a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just which Suikotsu are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:34.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I feel much better than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:39.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Half of me used to be in a daze.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:41.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was never sure when I would\nlose myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:45.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This time, it's different.\NI'm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:50.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean even if you\nnear the barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:52.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you won't change into\na saint?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:57.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. I came here to the base\nof Mt. Hakurei just to test it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:19:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That fool doctor hasn't appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:03.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:08.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-He looks the same, {\i1}but....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:16.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:23.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A bunch of orphans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:25.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll send you to the other world, too!\NDie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:40.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me, my Soul Collectors...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must hurry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:48.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Sacred Jewel shard is completely\nenshrouded in black light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:54.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suikotsu's heart has closed down.\NHe will likely harm the children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}D-Damn....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:22.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:31.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure in impure.\NImpure is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:35.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's happening?\NWhy can't I move?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:39.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}These damn kids are...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I seeing her face now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:01.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:48.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Sesshomaru can barely stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:52.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey {\i1}Suikotsu....{\i0}\NDon't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:54.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, you'd better hurry and\nget rid of that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.11,0:23:57.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm itching to kill this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.51,0:24:01.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the base of Mt. Hakurei, Inuyasha's\nolder brother, Sesshomaru, engages{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}in a death match with the Band of Seven.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:08.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Exposed Face of Truth"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.22,0:24:12.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just remembered.\NI already died once.
